<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  
  <title>LifeLeo - Tujitambue</title>
  @vite(['resources/css/app.scss', 'resources/js/app.js'])
</head>
<body data-bs-theme="light" class="source-serif-4-regular" id="htmlPage">
  <button role="button" id="btnToggleLight" style="cursor: pointer;">
    @svg('ic:baseline-wb-sunny')
  </button>
  <button role="button" id="btnToggleDark" style="cursor: pointer;">
    @svg('ic:round-nightlight')
  </button>
  <div class="container px-4 py-5" id="featured-3">
    <h1>LifeLeo</h1>
    <div class="col-md-7 p-lg-7 mx-auto my-5">
      <h1 class="display-6 fw-normal">Track Your Journey, One Day at a Time</h1>
      <p class="lead fw-normal">Capture life's moments with our simple, intuitive journaling app that helps you reflect on each day.</p>
    </div>
    <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom">What to Expect</h2>
    <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
      <div class="feature col">
        <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3">
          @svg('ic:twotone-pending-actions', {
            width: '1em',
            height: '1em',
          })
        </div>
        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Express your day in a click</h3>
        <p>Share your daily mood with a single tap. Happy, neutral, or challenging â€“ every feeling is valid and worth recording.</p>
        <a href="#" class="icon-link">
          Get Started
          <svg class="bi"><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature col">
        <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3">
          @svg('ic:outline-edit-note', {
            width: '1em',
            height: '1em',
          })
        </div>
        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Tell Your Story</h3>
        <p>Add context to your emotions. Whether it's a breakthrough moment or a quiet reflection, your words paint the full picture of your day.</p>
        <a href="#" class="icon-link">
          Get Started
          <svg class="bi"><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature col">
        <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3">
          @svg('ic:baseline-ssid-chart', {
            width: '1em',
            height: '1em',
          })
        </div>
        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Your History, Your Growth</h3>
        <p>Journey back through time with our calendar view. Rediscover your thoughts, track your emotional patterns, and witness your personal growth unfold.</p>
        <a href="#" class="icon-link">
          Get Started
          <svg class="bi"><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>